{"pages": [{"words": {"text": ["National", "Grid", "Community", "Relations", "Team", "JBP", "Freephone:", "0800", "073", "1047", "Third", "Floor,", "34", "Smith", "Square", "nationalgridteam@jbp.co.uk", "Westminster,", "London,", "SW1P", "3HL", "www.nationalgrid.com", "Councillor", "Robert", "Ward", "Selsdon", "and", "Addington", "Village", "ward,", "Croydon", "Council", "robert.ward@croydon.gov.uk", "20", "July", "2021", "Dear", "Councillor", "Ward", "Beddington", "to", "Rowdown", "cable", "replacement", "\u2013", "project", "update", "I", "thought", "it\u2019d", "be", "useful", "to", "send", "you", "an", "update", "about", "the", "replacement", "of", "the", "underground", "electricity", "cable", "We", "need", "to", "carry", "out", "our", "essential", "work", "to", "ensure", "we", "keep", "between", "Beddington", "and", "Rowdown", "substations.", "the", "transmission", "network", "in", "first-class", "working", "order", "and", "help", "meet", "future", "electricity", "demands.", "Our", "work", "represents", "a", "substantial", "investment", "in", "the", "region\u2019s", "power", "network.\u202f", "We\u2019re", "now", "in", "the", "latter", "stages", "of", "the", "project.", "However,", "due", "to", "delays", "because", "of", "the", "Covid-19", "pandemic", "and", "the", "knock-on", "effect", "to", "the", "supply", "chain,", "we", "expect", "our", "work", "will", "continue", "until", "Spring", "2022.", "The", "replacement", "is", "complete,", "and", "we\u2019ll", "now", "concentrate", "on", "testing", "the", "new", "cable.", "We\u2019ll", "take", "away", "the", "old", "cable,", "equipment,", "and", "materials", "from", "our", "working", "areas", "later", "this", "year", "and", "carry", "out", "some", "reinstatement", "work,", "including", "resurfacing", "and", "fence", "repairs.", "We\u2019ll", "then", "remove", "our", "site", "office", "cabins", "from", "Rowdown", "substation", "and", "stone", "chippings", "from", "a", "temporary", "haul", "road", "off", "Mickleham", "Way", "which", "leads", "to", "the", "substation.", "This", "will", "bring", "most", "of", "our", "work", "to", "an", "end", "with", "only", "minor", "electrical", "works", "continuing", "within", "the", "substations", "until", "Spring", "2022.", "None", "of", "our", "work", "will", "affect", "local", "electricity", "supplies.", "We\u2019ll", "keep", "our", "site", "neighbours", "informed", "as", "our", "work", "progresses", "on-site.", "I", "hope", "you", "find", "this", "this", "summary", "helpful.", "You", "can", "find", "more", "details", "about", "the", "project", "on", "our", "webpage", "https://www.nationalgrid.com/uk/electricity-transmission/infrastructure-projects/beddington-rowdown", "One", "final", "thing", "to", "mention", "is", "our", "Voices", "for", "A", "Green", "Future", "schools\u2019", "competition,", "which", "gives", "the", "next", "generation", "a", "voice", "on", "the", "journey", "to", "a", "clean", "energy", "future.", "We\u2019ve", "written", "to", "schools", "to", "encourage", "them", "to", "enter.", "The", "winners", "will", "have", "their", "speeches", "premiered", "at", "the", "UN", "Climate", "Change", "Conference", "later", "this", "year,", "of", "which", "we\u2019re", "the", "principal", "partner.", "If", "you\u2019d", "like", "to", "send", "it", "on", "to", "any", "local", "contacts", "here\u2019s", "the", "link", "for", "more", "information", "https://www.nationalgrid.com/cop26/voices-for-a-green-future/resources.", "If", "you", "have", "any", "queries", "about", "this", "scheme,", "please", "contact", "our", "Community", "Relations", "team", "on", "0800", "073", "1047", "or", "email", "nationalgridteam@jbp.co.uk.", "They\u2019re", "available", "daily", "from", "7am", "to", "7pm.", "Yours", "sincerely", "Lara", "Chilcott", "Project", "Manager", "National", "Grid", "National", "Grid", "Electricity", "Transmission", "plc", "1-3", "Strand,", "London", "WC2N", "5EH", "Registered", "in", "England", "and", "Wales,", "No", "2366977", "